snippet.title: Mario + Rabbids Kingdom Battle - Developer Diary E3 2017
snippet.description:
Discover the origins of the unexpected encounter between Mario and the irreverent Rabbids.

Mario teams up with the Rabbids in a turn-based combat adventure to save the Mushroom Kingdom! 
Mario + Rabbids® Kingdom Battle will be available exclusively for Nintendo Switch on August 29, 2017.

Join the team: http://www.mario-rabbids.com
